data.description: Welcome HOME!  Come see this 4 BDR 2 1/2 BA home located in a quiet neighborhood  in the heart of Baton Rouge. It's minutes away from I-10, I-12, Airline Hwy and Siegan Lane.  NO Flood Insurance required and voluntary HOA.  Seller will pay up to $2000.00 towards closing cost. Please provide preapproval or proof of funds letter with all offers along with a $500 deposit. The deposit will be held by the title company.  No Offers will be considered without the preapproval or proof of funds and deposit. Call for a private showing.
